Current unstable development version

Version 3 series
---------------
Future stable Semantically Versioned release

Files
-----
bsw.php - symbol encoding functions for PHP
	General BSW
	ISWA 2010
	Numbers
	Unicode PUA Integration

columns.css - div floating for columns

columns.php - script for text display

csw.php - Cartesian SignWriting processing for PHP

fsw.js - Modern SignWriting library for JavaScript

fsw.php - Formal and regular searching for PHP

glyph.php - symbol image script

glyphogram.php - cluster image script

image.php - main manipulation functions

spl.php - SignPuddle 1.6 legacy Conversion Library

spml.php - SignPuddle Markup Language
  read, pack, unpack
	
iswa - directory for fonts 

fonts of the ISWA are available online:
http://signpuddle.net/iswa/


Flavors
-------
SWIS for Web Servers - Requires web server with PHP5 and GD graphics library.
Install: unzip in public documents folder.

SWIS for Windows - Includes preconfigured Uniform Server web server.
Install: unzip anywhere (even on a USB drive)  and open the "Server_Start.bat" file.  In browser, open the location "http://localhost".

SWIS for Mac - Includes preconfigured MAMP web server.
Install: unzip to "MAMP" folder and place in the "Applications" folder.  Start the "MAMP.app" application in the "MAMP" folder.  In browser, open the location "http://localhost:8888".

